e you up in the middle of a session is getting old";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420429091";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14204290919";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1193411;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1193411";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:22:"Margareta_de_la_Orilla";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1202";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:14:"SpiritOfJackle";s:4:"text";s:848:"I tried to go in and you saw how well that&#039;s worked for me. But I&#039;m not going to spend the night going over specifics with one of the people on the site known for not changing their mind, no matter what. I liked the idea of this RP, and I did have fun at first. I also warned you guys in the beginning about my schedule, and that I live a military lifestyle. I made sure to point out that Kyubi or Portent would have been a better choice than me because of that. I&#039;m sorry that I can&#039;t dedicate a portion of my time to anything much, it sucks. I&#039;ve seen my girlfriend one week in a years time, I&#039;ve seen my family only a bit longer than that. My focuses will never be on an RP when there&#039;s other stuff I feel more obligated to do. I&#039;ve had to cut on a lot more things than I&#039;ve wanted to because of it. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420429656";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6472dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14204296497";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#2aa1a7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1193423;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1193423";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:14:"SpiritOfJackle";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1058";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:22:"Margareta_de_la_Orilla";s:4:"text";s:192:"Well...As I said, this is a thing where you need to put things in to get things out. I would suggest leaving the campaign if you can&#039;t do that, as that would relieve strain for the group.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420429942";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14204299404";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1193425;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1193425";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:14:"SpiritOfJackle";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1058";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:22:"Margareta_de_la_Orilla";s:4:"text";s:93:"If, however, you are confident you can get something out of this campaign, then you may stay.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420429960";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14204299610";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1193427;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1193427";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"37";s:6:"handle";s:22:"Margareta_de_la_Orilla";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1202";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:14:"SpiritOfJackle";s:4:"text";s:18:"Then I&#039;ll go.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420430023";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6472dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14204300166";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#2aa1a7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}}